Вакансія від 17 березня 2020
Sales manager
15 000 – 20 000 грн
Brainy · Агенція
Пошук персоналу, HR;
10–50 співробітників
Київ
Повна зайнятість, дистанційна робота, готові взяти студента.
Досвід роботи від 1 року.
Опис вакансії
About the companyBrainy is specializing in custom-built recruitment of IT specialists for EU, USA, Canada, Australia and Asia companies. We are the group of recruitment professionals wish to expand companies worldwide with high-qualified and open-minded IT Engineers. Main industries we are working with are web-development, e-commerce, telecom, banking, financial services, entertainment, media, retail, healthcare, logistics etc.OverviewWe are looking for a qualified Business Development Manager who will be responsible for closing deals with new customers as well as developing long-term relationships. Energetic and self motivated person, able to identify and develop new business prospects from multiple sources.Responsibilities● Investigate potential B2B Clients● Execute proper introduction● Develop long-term trusted relationships with new and existing Clients● Individual approach to each customer (existing and potential)● Negotiate, conclude contracts, control billing● Managing both our existing sales methods and developing new business solutions● Timely and accurate reporting● Active cooperation with recruiters and business developers teamRequirements● English (С1 or C2)● At least 2 years experience in B2B sales● Selling skills● Internet search skills● Strong business communication skills (verbal, written, presentations)● Time management and planning skills● Ability to think creatively and drive innovative ideas to a BizDev teamWould Be An Advantage● IT market knowledge (technologies, competitors)● IT recruitment market knowledge● Result oriented● Self — starter● Fast learner● OrganizedWhat We Offer● Competitive salary + bonuses● Free working schedule;● Remote working;
